## What Is DataTools Pro?

DataTools Pro is a **Salesforce-connected platform that brings Salesforce and data cloud professionals together**. It manages an organization's metrics, data dictionary, entity relationships, migrations, and report governance — all within a single shared data model.

**Core value proposition:**
> DataTools Pro helps Salesforce administrators, data analysts, analytics professionals, and business teams collaborate more effectively by maintaining a living, connected documentation and governance layer on top of their Salesforce org.

